1
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,211
Yujin, it’s time to wake up.

2
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,434
Just a little longer.

3
00:00:53,710 --> 00:00:56,170
You’re going to be late again.

4
00:01:00,994 --> 00:01:02,994
I don’t want to go to school.

5
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:08,132
I just want to stay with you.

6
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:21,595
Come to the café after school. Let’s have dinner together.

7
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:39,576
What’s going on?
You looked like you were dying just a few days ago.

8
00:01:41,960 --> 00:01:42,913
No way.

9
00:01:44,481 --> 00:01:47,995
Hey, is it true? Are you finally dating?

10
00:01:49,762 --> 00:01:55,000
Wow, you actually made it. Congrats, Seo Yujin.
You have to introduce him to me sometime.

11
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,425
We’ll see.

12
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,354
You’re here?

13
00:02:37,148 --> 00:02:38,005
Yeah.

14
00:02:39,077 --> 00:02:41,586
Is there anything I can help with?

15
00:02:43,808 --> 00:02:47,434
No, it’s okay. Sit down. I’ll take care of it.

16
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:00,934
Drink this while you wait.

17
00:03:04,712 --> 00:03:06,000
Thanks.

18
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:15,475
Mm,
the coffee here is really good.

19
00:03:16,129 --> 00:03:20,000
Right? I guess the owner makes it himself.

20
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:28,360
But...
isn’t the owner really attractive?

21
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:31,384
I know. You should try talking to him.

22
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:40,352
I think I’m going to buy some beans.

23
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:50,000
Excuse me, could you tell me what beans were used for the coffee I just had? It was really good.

24
00:03:50,324 --> 00:03:57,925
Yes. What you had today was this blend. It has a little acidity, with a sweet finish, so it’s easy to drink.

25
00:03:58,025 --> 00:04:00,426
Oh, that makes sense.

26
00:04:00,426 --> 00:04:03,610
Could I make something similar with this at home?

27
00:04:07,592 --> 00:04:11,439
He’s so kind and good-looking.

28
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:14,797
Right...
I bet he has someone.

29
00:04:16,107 --> 00:04:18,152
He’s not wearing a ring, though.

30
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,175
Yujin, what’s wrong?

31
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:52,660
Huh?
Why is the door locked?

32
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:14,329
We should probably stop now.

33
00:06:15,278 --> 00:06:18,571
Sir,
are you in there?

34
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:16,461
I want to get matching rings with you.

35
00:07:17,036 --> 00:07:18,036
Rings?

36
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:22,734
Okay. I’d like that.

37
00:07:31,955 --> 00:07:34,854
I’ll have to save up.

38
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,000
Don’t tell me...

39
00:07:39,714 --> 00:07:43,606
You’re not thinking of doing that weird photoshoot job again, are you?

40
00:07:46,599 --> 00:07:49,329
It’s not a weird place, hyung.

41
00:07:57,639 --> 00:08:00,753
No... that’s not the point.

42
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:08,773
I...

43
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,877
I don’t like other people seeing you like that.

44
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,977
It’s just...

45
00:08:25,307 --> 00:08:27,332
I wanted to do something for you, too.

46
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:41,028
If it’s something you really want to do,
I won’t try to stop you.

47
00:08:41,385 --> 00:08:45,147
But if you’re doing it because of me, don’t.

48
00:08:49,603 --> 00:08:52,209
I’ll take care of the rings.

49
00:08:55,796 --> 00:08:57,814
Let’s go look at them together.

50
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,977
Okay. I will.

51
00:09:33,931 --> 00:09:35,350
What?

52
00:09:36,298 --> 00:09:39,361
Nothing. I was just looking at you.

53
00:09:42,894 --> 00:09:44,634
You’re supposed to be watching the movie.

54
00:09:46,777 --> 00:09:48,912
I am watching.

55
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,786
What about the movie?

56
00:10:41,242 --> 00:10:43,182
We can watch it again.
